      "source_repo": "ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "\ud83d\ude43   A delightful community-driven (with 2,400+ contributors) framework for managing your zsh configuration. Includes 300+ optional plugins (rails, git, macOS, hub, docker, homebrew, node, php, python, etc), 140+ themes to spice up your morning, and an auto-update tool that makes it easy to keep up with the latest updates from the community."
